data.title: Sussex County Sports Hall of Fame
meta_keywords: Sussex County Sports Hall of Fame
data.meta_description: The Sussex County Sports Hall of Fame (SCSHOF)honors athletes, coaches and benefactors who either lived in Sussex County or trained in the county, and whose extraordinary performance qualified them for induction.
data.text:
The Class of 2009 SCSHOF Inductee Dinner was held on Friday, November 6, 2009

All of the inductees were introduced by an individual who influenced their athletic career, and then each inductee give an overview of their athletic history and those who helped them achieve success.

Congratulations to all new Inductees!

* Inductee Photos: We wish to add photos to past SCSHOF Inductee profiles. If you have a photo of a SCSHOF Inductee please send it as an e-mail attachment by clicking HERE or mail it to the SCSHOF Attention: Web Master.

* The site now has a search engine. Scroll down and type in the name you are looking for and select the information you wish to view.

Honoring Athletes, Coaches and Benefactors whose outstanding performance has earned them the right to be enshrined in the

Sussex County Sports Hall of Fame!
